"title": "6756: union with Christ, significance of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6756: union with christ, significance of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The union between Jesus Christ and believers is the basis for all exhortation to faithful, holy living, as well as to sharing in all his benefits.</p>\n<h2>For the believer</h2>\n<h3>Identification with Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:40\">MAT 10:40</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:5\">MAT 18:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:40\">MAT 25:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:1\">EPH 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1\">PHP 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>The experience of being in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:17\">2CO 5:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:20\">JHN 14:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:5\">2CO 13:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:20\">GAL 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:14-Eph3:19\">EPH 3:14–3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>Conformity to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1-Col3:4\">COL 3:1–3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:24\">MAT 16:24</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:34\">MRK 8:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:23\">LUK 9:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:5\">ROM 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:15-1Cor6:17\">1CO 6:15–6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor4:10\">2CO 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:6\">EPH 2:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:10-Phil3:11\">PHP 3:10–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet4:13\">1PE 4:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:6\">1JN 2:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:28\">1JN 2:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:24\">1JN 3:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:20\">1JN 5:20</a></p>\n<h3>Righteousness in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:23-Rom4:25\">ROM 4:23–4:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">1CO 1:30</a></p>\n<h3>Blessing in Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:3-Eph1:14\">EPH 1:3–1:14</a></strong></p>\n<h2>For the church</h2>\n<h3>In persecution</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:5\">ACT 9:3–9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6-Acts22:8\">ACT 22:6–22:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14\">ACT 26:14</a></p>\n<h3>In service</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12\">1CO 12:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:8\">ROM 12:4–12:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:27\">1CO 12:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22-Eph1:23\">EPH 1:22–1:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:28-Eph5:30\">EPH 5:28–5:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a></p>",
